snippet.title: Mochi's Cosy Quest reveal trailer
snippet.description:
Mochi's Cosy Quest is a cosy 3D puzzle game where you play as a capybara!!! Explore 6 different magical worlds floating islands, giant toys, a tropical paradise, there's so much to see!

Wishlist now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3283460/Mochis_Cosy_Quest/
